1
00:00:02,312 --> 00:00:05,671
[One year ago]

2
00:00:06,699 --> 00:00:08,810
<i>I don't have time for this, Jae Min,</i>

3
00:00:08,810 --> 00:00:12,042
<i>so just answer my question.</i>

4
00:00:12,042 --> 00:00:14,431
<i>Is it true?</i>

5
00:00:14,431 --> 00:00:16,266
<i>Was there something between you two?</i>

6
00:00:16,926 --> 00:00:19,013
<i>I don't see what you're getting at.</i>

7
00:00:19,013 --> 00:00:22,639
<i>Haven't you heard?
There's even a petition to kick you out.</i>

8
00:00:22,639 --> 00:00:24,179
<i>What I'm asking you is,</i>

9
00:00:24,179 --> 00:00:27,445
<i>if there really were any mutual feelings...</i>

10
00:00:27,445 --> 00:00:30,089
<i>between you and that idol.</i>

11
00:00:31,752 --> 00:00:33,525
<i>Huh?</i>

12
00:00:33,525 --> 00:00:36,579
<i>You're a contestant, what were you thinking?</i>

13
00:00:36,579 --> 00:00:38,765
<i>Whatever.</i>

14
00:00:38,765 --> 00:00:40,645
<i>I can't believe you got into a scandal!</i>

15
00:00:40,645 --> 00:00:42,965
<i>The agency...</i>

16
00:00:42,965 --> 00:00:44,252
<i>just made a statement.</i>

17
00:00:44,252 --> 00:00:45,485
<i>What are they saying?</i>

18
00:00:45,485 --> 00:00:47,192
<i>The romance rumors are entirely false,</i>

19
00:00:47,192 --> 00:00:51,432
<i>and Jae Min's persistent attention
caused our artist discomfort...</i>

20
00:00:51,432 --> 00:00:53,285
<i>and even fear.</i>

21
00:00:53,285 --> 00:00:55,101
<i>That's it.</i>

22
00:00:56,752 --> 00:00:59,039
<i>Wait, what?</i>

23
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:00,952
<i>Fear?</i>

24
00:01:00,952 --> 00:01:04,648
<i>This could come off as stalking.</i>

25
00:01:04,648 --> 00:01:06,574
<i>What do we do?</i>

26
00:01:08,639 --> 00:01:10,692
<i>Sir!</i>

27
00:01:10,692 --> 00:01:13,999
<i>Sir!</i>

28
00:01:35,285 --> 00:01:37,376
It's fine.

29
00:01:42,592 --> 00:01:44,039
Your number.

30
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,478
Hey.

31
00:01:45,478 --> 00:01:47,649
I don't give my number out to just anyone.

32
00:01:47,649 --> 00:01:49,485
That's not who I am.

33
00:01:49,485 --> 00:01:52,771
- I don't know what you thought of me...
- Give.

34
00:01:54,392 --> 00:01:56,081
Give me please.

35
00:01:58,552 --> 00:02:00,422
That was bold.

36
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,492
Hey, wait!

37
00:02:12,492 --> 00:02:14,266
Hey!

38
00:02:14,859 --> 00:02:18,952
You should... return your tray.

39
00:02:18,952 --> 00:02:22,559
And did he just take my number and run off?

40
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:24,864
Who even does that? I need his, too.

41
00:02:48,192 --> 00:02:50,829
[One year ago]
<i>- Break a leg! - Good luck!</i>

42
00:02:54,785 --> 00:02:56,361
<i>What's that?</i>

43
00:02:56,975 --> 00:02:59,679
<i>Oh, this? Just a lucky charm.</i>

44
00:02:59,679 --> 00:03:02,105
<i>I passed every audition I took with it on.</i>

45
00:03:02,105 --> 00:03:03,752
<i>So I always keep it on me.</i>

46
00:03:03,752 --> 00:03:05,105
<i>Really?</i>

47
00:03:05,105 --> 00:03:06,385
<i>Do you want to try it on?</i>

48
00:03:06,385 --> 00:03:08,086
<i>Can I?</i>

49
00:03:21,545 --> 00:03:23,401
<i>The final stage is starting soon!</i>

50
00:03:23,401 --> 00:03:24,843
<i>Let's go.</i>

51
00:03:26,145 --> 00:03:28,825
Hyun Jae, who is it?

52
00:03:28,825 --> 00:03:29,853
Is something wrong?

53
00:03:29,853 --> 00:03:31,678
Oh, it's nothing.

54
00:03:38,365 --> 00:03:40,919
- Hello?
<i>- Hello.</i>

55
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:44,072
I'm... uh...

56
00:03:44,072 --> 00:03:46,159
the guy from...

57
00:03:49,632 --> 00:03:51,356
Hey.

58
00:03:51,356 --> 00:03:54,032
You were pretty close by.

59
00:03:54,032 --> 00:03:55,621
Yeah.

60
00:03:56,579 --> 00:03:58,499
This.

61
00:03:58,499 --> 00:04:00,092
What is it?

62
00:04:00,092 --> 00:04:02,125
Take it.

63
00:04:02,125 --> 00:04:03,785
But what is it?

64
00:04:03,785 --> 00:04:06,712
- T-shirt.
- A tee...

65
00:04:06,712 --> 00:04:09,019
Ah, no, you don't need to.

66
00:04:09,019 --> 00:04:10,685
I'm sorry.

67
00:04:10,685 --> 00:04:13,952
No, it's really fine. I'm serious.

68
00:04:13,952 --> 00:04:15,581
Take it.

69
00:04:16,485 --> 00:04:17,872
If you're really sorry,

70
00:04:17,872 --> 00:04:20,005
you could buy me dinner instead.

71
00:04:20,005 --> 00:04:22,012
Take it!

72
00:04:22,012 --> 00:04:24,045
Ah, wait!

73
00:04:24,045 --> 00:04:25,621
Hey!

74
00:04:29,478 --> 00:04:32,057
I don't even know what his name is.

75
00:04:43,732 --> 00:04:46,421
[Ketchup]

76
00:04:49,259 --> 00:04:51,875
- Good work.
- Good work.

77
00:04:52,905 --> 00:04:56,128
- Great work.
- Good night.

78
00:04:57,132 --> 00:04:59,911
- Good work.
- Great work.

79
00:05:09,612 --> 00:05:11,037
Huh?

80
00:05:11,785 --> 00:05:13,393
Excuse me.

81
00:05:14,425 --> 00:05:16,131
Good night.

82
00:05:20,365 --> 00:05:22,525
[Ye Eun]

83
00:05:40,883 --> 00:05:42,499
<i>Hey, Yoon Soo An,
are you trying to tick me off?</i>

84
00:05:42,499 --> 00:05:45,285
<i>Come over right now before I lose it.</i>

85
00:05:45,285 --> 00:05:46,577
I can't.

86
00:05:46,577 --> 00:05:50,100
<i>You didn't answer my texts! Where are you?</i>

87
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:52,436
- I'm at home.
<i>- What?</i>

88
00:05:53,152 --> 00:05:55,002
I saw him.

89
00:06:15,832 --> 00:06:18,036
You should get back to training.

90
00:06:18,845 --> 00:06:20,299
I can't be an idol.

91
00:06:20,299 --> 00:06:23,585
Why not? You didn't do anything wrong.

92
00:06:23,585 --> 00:06:26,345
You shouldn't have stepped down.

93
00:06:26,345 --> 00:06:28,503
We should've told the truth.

94
00:06:28,503 --> 00:06:30,559
You went out with him because he liked you.

95
00:06:30,559 --> 00:06:32,726
How could he just frame you as a stalker?

96
00:06:32,726 --> 00:06:34,579
What a jerk.

97
00:06:47,505 --> 00:06:50,949
I think... I saw Soo An.

98
00:06:51,945 --> 00:06:53,672
At the studio.

99
00:06:55,290 --> 00:06:57,585
I think he's working as a staff member.

100
00:06:57,585 --> 00:06:59,279
What? No way.

101
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:01,588
He's the ace of Unicorn. He'd be practicing.

102
00:07:01,588 --> 00:07:03,298
Why would he be working?

103
00:07:04,052 --> 00:07:05,955
Why not just ask him?

104
00:07:09,825 --> 00:07:12,392
[Soo An, can we call?]

105
00:07:19,265 --> 00:07:20,765
<i>Can I?</i>

106
00:07:38,745 --> 00:07:40,259
- Whoa!
- What? What is it?

107
00:07:40,259 --> 00:07:41,479
Hey, where did you get this?

108
00:07:41,479 --> 00:07:43,185
It's from a luxury brand, right?

109
00:07:43,185 --> 00:07:45,892
- Uh, no, it's not.
- Yes, it is!

110
00:07:45,892 --> 00:07:48,172
It must've cost a fortune.

111
00:07:48,172 --> 00:07:50,465
- What, really?
- Did you buy it yourself?

112
00:07:50,465 --> 00:07:52,514
- No.
- Did you steal it, then?

113
00:07:52,514 --> 00:07:55,104
- No!
- Well?

114
00:07:56,088 --> 00:07:58,298
How much is it?

115
00:08:03,088 --> 00:08:05,048
What?

116
00:08:05,048 --> 00:08:07,704
- 850,000 won?
- 850,000 won.

117
00:08:08,534 --> 00:08:11,078
- What do I do?
- Do what?

118
00:08:12,568 --> 00:08:14,726
I can't do this. Wait here!

119
00:08:20,761 --> 00:08:22,747
You think they'll take it back?

120
00:08:29,927 --> 00:08:31,574
Oh, you're here.

121
00:08:31,574 --> 00:08:34,072
Well, look who it is!

122
00:08:36,381 --> 00:08:37,481
I'm back.

123
00:08:37,481 --> 00:08:39,701
You did a great job.

124
00:08:39,701 --> 00:08:40,768
It's nothing, sir.

125
00:08:40,768 --> 00:08:44,066
We've been waiting for you.

126
00:08:44,066 --> 00:08:47,388
We've got big plans for you, so rest up.

127
00:08:47,388 --> 00:08:49,234
Manager Kang, take him home.

128
00:08:49,234 --> 00:08:50,683
Yes, sir.

129
00:08:50,683 --> 00:08:52,030
Let's go.

130
00:08:55,141 --> 00:08:57,914
What? Are you waiting for someone?

131
00:08:57,914 --> 00:08:59,504
No, of course not.

132
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:03,021
Don't slack off just because the group's done.

133
00:09:03,021 --> 00:09:05,054
Plenty of eyes are on you.

134
00:09:05,054 --> 00:09:06,958
I know, sir.

135
00:09:09,614 --> 00:09:11,130
Let's go.

136
00:09:13,268 --> 00:09:17,404
<i>At the tone, please record your message.</i>

137
00:09:19,108 --> 00:09:21,519
Come on, answer already.

138
00:09:28,522 --> 00:09:30,385
Oh, hey!

139
00:09:31,248 --> 00:09:32,971
Hey, wait!

140
00:10:11,482 --> 00:10:14,148
[Notice]
[No outsiders are currently allowed in]

141
00:10:58,109 --> 00:11:01,379
<i>Working hard to meet you on stage.</i>

142
00:11:12,829 --> 00:11:14,459
Oh!

143
00:11:18,189 --> 00:11:19,940
Hey!

144
00:11:23,969 --> 00:11:25,640
Hello.

145
00:11:26,262 --> 00:11:28,649
Did I scare you?

146
00:11:28,649 --> 00:11:31,629
You scared me with how jumpy you are.

147
00:11:31,629 --> 00:11:34,444
I just wanted to see you about this.

148
00:11:34,444 --> 00:11:36,280
Is this an expensive shirt?

149
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,855
Expensive?

150
00:11:37,855 --> 00:11:40,349
Um... It's just...

151
00:11:40,349 --> 00:11:42,115
Normal.

152
00:11:42,115 --> 00:11:43,949
Normal?

153
00:11:43,949 --> 00:11:45,755
I'm sorry.

154
00:11:45,755 --> 00:11:47,416
For what?

155
00:11:47,416 --> 00:11:49,358
You don't like it?

156
00:11:49,358 --> 00:11:51,753
Ah, this shirt is...

157
00:11:51,753 --> 00:11:53,881
Expensive. Too expensive.

158
00:11:53,881 --> 00:11:55,620
You know?

159
00:11:56,884 --> 00:11:58,736
It's nothing.

160
00:11:58,736 --> 00:12:01,289
I said that's okay.

161
00:12:01,289 --> 00:12:02,615
But...

162
00:12:02,615 --> 00:12:04,415
Let's take this back.

163
00:12:04,415 --> 00:12:06,809
Take... back?

164
00:12:06,809 --> 00:12:09,882
Refund. Okay?

165
00:12:09,882 --> 00:12:11,789
But...

166
00:12:11,789 --> 00:12:13,489
I didn't even wear it much.

167
00:12:13,489 --> 00:12:15,473
It's basically brand-new.

168
00:12:24,979 --> 00:12:26,626
<i>Have a bite.</i>

169
00:12:26,626 --> 00:12:28,790
Aw, dang it.

170
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:30,640
Kim Hyun Jae.

171
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:37,593
Well, now what?

172
00:12:37,593 --> 00:12:40,103
- It's okay.
- No, no!

173
00:12:40,822 --> 00:12:43,049
I'm not comfortable with this.

174
00:12:43,049 --> 00:12:45,429
Let me see what I have on me.

175
00:12:49,895 --> 00:12:51,773
I'm empty-handed now,

176
00:12:51,773 --> 00:12:53,504
but I'll do anything.

177
00:12:55,736 --> 00:12:57,315
Your body.

178
00:12:58,596 --> 00:13:00,105
Come again?

179
00:13:08,869 --> 00:13:10,256
You can pay me back...

180
00:13:10,256 --> 00:13:11,991
with your body.

181
00:13:28,062 --> 00:13:29,202
[Hotel LUXE]

182
00:13:29,202 --> 00:13:31,169
This doesn't feel right.

183
00:13:31,169 --> 00:13:33,522
What is he even thinking?

184
00:13:33,522 --> 00:13:36,534
You left this for me to find, didn't you?

185
00:13:38,443 --> 00:13:40,249
Why did you cut me off?

186
00:13:40,249 --> 00:13:41,782
We used each other for fame.

187
00:13:41,782 --> 00:13:43,949
You even got to debut. Isn't that enough?

188
00:13:43,949 --> 00:13:45,806
Want me to warm it up?

189
00:13:48,329 --> 00:13:50,675
Do you really feel nothing towards me?

